      "value": "<p>You convince a creature you can see within range that it canâ€™t escape impending doom. The target must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the target believes any attacks that miss it are actually hitting it. Each time a creature misses an attack against the target, the target takes 1d6 psychic damage. At the end of each of its turns, the target can make another Wisdom saving throw. On a success, the spell ends.<br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 2nd.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
